        },
        "fq_12": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Is the warranty actually any good?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes — and we deliberately structured it to outlast the payback period:</p><ul><li><strong>5 years</strong> on the motor (the most expensive component)</li><li><strong>2 years</strong> on all parts (electronics, rails, fans, lighting)</li><li><strong>1 year</strong> of full unit servicing — included, on us</li></ul><p>By the time the motor warranty ends, the unit has already saved you ~$1,800 in energy. Everything past Year 5 is pure savings — and you're still covered for the most expensive part.</p><p>Real Australian support team — you'll talk to a human, not a chatbot.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
